thread.title: Protests against civilian killings, rape of minor erupt in Indian Kashmir

title: Protests against civilian killings, rape of minor erupt in Indian Kashmir
text:
Protests against civilian killings, rape of minor erupt in Indian Kashmir 1:03pm BST - 00:45 
Violent protests erupt in Indian Kashmir over the killing of civilians and the rape of an eight-year-old girl in the strife-torn state. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
